data.description: This gem of a home is waiting for new owners!! Absolutely gorgeous hard wood floors throughout the main level. Bright and open covered front porch with light fixture and fan. Kitchen has everything you need with tile floors, cupboard space, and appliances. Each bedroom has a ceiling fan, with one bedroom carpeted and the other wood flooring. Unfinished basement is perfect for storage or creating a space for working out. Out back, you'll find a beautiful deck with stairs that lead into the yard. Mature trees and fencing give a sense of privacy so you can enjoy your space. There is a single detached garage space. Come check it out and schedule a showing today!
